No. D-2557. In the Matter of Discipline of Thomas Dale Grabinski. 562 U.S. 816, 131 S. Ct. 408,

178 L. Ed. 2d 272,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7500. October 4, 2010.

Thomas Dale Grabin-ski, of Globe, Arizona, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, re*273quiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
